<text top="597" left="157" width="273" height="21" font="2">五、实践性环节学习考核要求</text>
<text top="593" left="157" width="16" height="28" font="4">1.</text>
<text top="597" left="173" width="467" height="22" font="3">含实践的课程及实践所占学分：心理测量与评估（</text>
<text top="593" left="640" width="11" height="28" font="4">2</text>
